The Board and Staff of Midsummer Musical Retreat invite you to register online for MMR <%= @year %>. 
The online system is designed to save paper and staff time.   We will be happy to help you through the process.  
Complete details about the program and faculty are on our website, 
http://musicalretreat.org

You can access online registration from the registration home page: 
http://home.mmr-registration.org/registration/index

Emails will be sent to you from registrar@musicalretreat.org.
Please set your email filter to accept this address.

Your email address will be your personal ID.
You will need to keep track of your email and password to access your account information online.
Registration will be open from January 1 to February 15, <%= @year %>.

If you registered online last year, go to the 
registration home page http://home.mmr-registration.org/registration/index,
and log in using 
your email and password from last year. If you have forgotten your password, you may request a new one.
You will not be able to complete the registration form until January 1, 
but you can visit the site and change your password immediately, if you choose to do so.


If this is your first year to register online, you will need to set up an account. 
You will not be able to complete the registration form until January 1, but you can visit the 
site and establish your ID and password immediately, if you choose to do so.  Please follow the following steps:

  * Go to the registration home page at http://home.mmr-registration.org/registration/index
  * Click on "Create New Account," and enter your email. Confirm it by re-typing as indicated
  * A temporary password will be sent to your email address
  * You may immediately return to the registration site and change the password.  
       Please be sure to copy in your temporary password exactly, including all 
       dashes, and making sure you type upper case and lower case letters exactly 
       as they appear in the email.
  * When registration opens on January 1 you will use that email and password 
       to register.

